{{Wireless embedded system |brand=ASUS |model=RT-AC85 |revision=U |upc=0889349349625 |asin=B01LX0WM1U;JP;, |price=220 |series=AC2600 |est_release_date=09/13/2016 |fcc_date=07/13/2017 |manuf_country=China |is_manuf=No |manuf=Edimax |manuf_model= |manuf_rev= |availability=Japan |type=wireless router |fcc_id=NDD9568791701 |pcb_id=1244-01001091-50Z |pwr_v=12 |pwr_amp=1.5 |pwr_conn=barrel |cpu1_brand=MediaTek |cpu1_model=MT7621A |cpu1_cspeed=880 |cpu1_cores=2 |fla1=128 |fla1_brand=Winbond |fla1_model=NAND |ram1=128 |ram1_brand=Winbond |ram1_model=DDR3 |expansion_if_types=USB 3.0 |expansion_usb_num=1 |jtag= |serial=yes,, 4-pad header,, |wi1_chip1_brand=MediaTek |wi1_chip1_model=MT7615E |wi1_802dot11_protocols=bgn |wi1_ant_conn=U.FL |wi1_txchains=4 |wi1_rxchains=4 |wi1_sstreams=4 |wi2_chip1_brand=MediaTek |wi2_chip1_model=MT7615E |wi2_802dot11_protocols=an+ac |wi2_ant_conn=U.FL |wi2_txchains=4 |wi2_rxchains=4 |wi2_sstreams=4 |eth_none= |eth_cpu=true |sw_cpu=true |lan_speed=1G |lan_ports=4 |wan_ports=1 |addl_chips= |flags=MU-MIMO |tp_firmware=Padavan ? |802dot11_protocols=abgn+ac |default_ssid=ASUS_XX_2G,ASUS_XX_5G |default_ssid_regex=^ASUS_XX_2G$,,,^ASUS_XX_5G$ |default_ip=192.168.1.1 |default_user=admin |default_pass=admin |oui= |oui_eth= }} {{TagLine|Dual Band Wireless-AC2600 Gigabit Router}} :[https://www.asus.com/Networking/RT-AC85U/ Product page] {{•}} [https://www.asus.com/jp/Networking/RT-AC85U/ Product page] (JP) :[http://www.asus.com/pl/supportonly/RT-AC85U/HelpDesk_Download/ Support page] (PL) {{•}} [http://stw.asus.com/download/download.aspx?model=RT-AC85U&SLanguage=en-en&product=11&os=8 Download FW/GPL] "1244-01001091-50Z" and "1639" is silkscreened on the board. {{see also|ASUS RT-AC65U|ASUS|Edimax}} ===Specifications=== [https://www.asus.com/jp/News/MqAfpb2iApOIgwST News & Press release] (JP) (+ [[ASUS USB-AC68]]) :• CPU: [[MediaTek]] MT7621A @880MHz Dual Core SoC :• Memory: RAM 128MB (DDR3), Flash 128MB (NAND) :• WLAN: 4T4R 802.11ac 5GHz (1734 Mbps) :+ 4T4R 802.11n 2.4GHz (800 Mbps), MU-MIMO :• Ports: 1x WAN GbE, 4x LAN GbE, 1x USB 3.0 :• Power Supply: DC 12V / 2A :• Dimensions: 205 x 31 x 148 mm (WxDxH) :• Weight: 345 g ===Forum threads=== *[https://www.snbforums.com/threads/asus-rt-ac85u-dual-band-wireless-ac2600-gigabit-router.35188/ ''Asus RT-AC85U Dual-Band Wireless-AC2600 Gigabit Router'' on '''SNB''' forums] *[http://wl500g.info/showthread.php?33775-Asus-RT-AC85U-RT-AC58U-RT-AC53-and-RT-AC1200GU ''Asus RT-AC85U, RT-AC58U, RT-AC53 and RT-AC1200GU'' on '''wl500g.info'''] :[[ASUS RT-AC85U]] (Wireless-AC2600) - FW 3.0.0.4.380.5971 (2016/09/13) :[[MediaTek]] MT7621A/MT7615E (iPA/eLNA), RAM/Flash 128MB, USB 3.0 *[https://forum.lede-project.org/t/new-router-asus-rt-ac85u/1652 ''Asus RT-AC85U'' on '''Lede-Project''' forums] ===GPL Info=== {{SCollapse|GPL info >> • |
export RT-AC85U := IPV6SUPP=y HTTPS=y MIPS32=r2 RALINK=y MT7621=y 
  BBEXTRAS=y USBEXTRAS=y EBTABLES=y SAMBA3=y MEDIASRV=y RTAC85U=y 
  MODEMPIN=y PARENTAL2=y ACCEL_PPTPD=y PRINTER=y USB="USB" MODEM=y 
  APP="network" AUTODICT=y LANWAN_LED=y BUILD_NAME="RT-AC85U" SHP=y 
  ODMPID=y DUAL_TRX=y LED_ALL=y NEW_RGDM=y RA_SKU_IN_DRV=y VPNC=y 
  OPENVPN=y DUMP_OOPS_MSG=y DEBUGFS=y REBOOT_SCHEDULE=y \
	WEBDAV=y CLOUDSYNC=y SWEBDAVCLIENT=y DROPBOXCLIENT=y 
        FTPCLIENT=y SAMBACLIENT=y SSH=y \
	NTFS="tuxera" HFS="tuxera" DISK_MONITOR=y \
	TIMEMACHINE=y MDNS=y EMAIL=y \
	ATED122=y \
	XHCI=y ATEUSB3_FORCE=y \
	BLINK_LED=y BTN_WPS_ALLLED=y \
	BOOT_FLASH_TYPE=NAND MTK_NAND=y \
	DRAM=128M \
	FIRST_IF=MT7615E SECOND_IF=MT7615E RALINK_DFS=y \
	QAM256_2G=y MUMIMO_5G=y UBI=y UBIFS=y PSISTLOG=y \
	TEMPROOTFS=y WPSMULTIBAND=y NEW_USER_LOW_RSSI=y \
	NEWSSID_REV2=y GETREALIP=y ATCOVER=y LAN50=y \
	EXTRA_KERNEL_CONFIGS="MT7621_BAUDRATE=57600 
        RT2880_DRAM_128M=y UBOOT_CMDLINE=y MODEL_RTAC85U=y 
        SMART_CARRIER_SENSE_SUPPORT=y MT_DFS_SUPPORT=y 
        DUAL_TRX=y FIRST_IF_IPAELNA=y SECOND_IF_IPAELNA=y"

export RT-AC85U_BASE := IPV6SUPP=y HTTPS=y MIPS32=r2 RALINK=y MT7621=y 
  BBEXTRAS=y USBEXTRAS=y EBTABLES=y SAMBA3=y MEDIASRV=y PARENTAL2=y 
  ACCEL_PPTPD=y  USB="USB"  AUTODICT=y LANWAN_LED=y SHP=y RTAC85U=y 
  ODMPID=y DUAL_TRX=y LED_ALL=y NEW_RGDM=y RA_SKU_IN_DRV=y OPENVPN=y 
  VPNC=y DUMP_OOPS_MSG=y DEBUGFS=y BWDPI=y REBOOT_SCHEDULE=y SSH=y \
    NTFS="tuxera" EXT4FS=y DISK_MONITOR=y MDNS=y EMAIL=y SYSSTATE=y 
      USB_SWAP=y \
    ATED122=y MTK_8021X3000=y \
    XHCI=y ATEUSB3_FORCE=y \
    BLINK_LED=y BTN_WPS_ALLLED=y \
    BOOT_FLASH_TYPE=NAND MTK_NAND=y \
    DRAM=128M \
    FIRST_IF=MT7615E SECOND_IF=MT7615E RALINK_DFS=y MTK_MUMIMO=y 
      MUMIMO_5G=y QAM256_2G=y \
    UBI=y UBIFS=y PSISTLOG=y \
    TEMPROOTFS=y WPSMULTIBAND=y \
    NEW_USER_LOW_RSSI=y NEWSSID_REV2=y GETREALIP=y ATCOVER=y LAN50=y

export RT-AC85U := $(RT-AC85U_BASE) HFS="tuxera"
export RT-AC85U += BUILD_NAME="RT-AC85U" 
  EXTRA_KERNEL_CONFIGS="MT7621_BAUDRATE=57600 RT2880_DRAM_128M=y 
  UBOOT_CMDLINE=y MODEL_RTAC85U=y SMART_CARRIER_SENSE_SUPPORT=y 
  MT_DFS_SUPPORT=y DUAL_TRX=y FIRST_IF_IPAELNA=y SECOND_IF_IPAELNA=y"
export RT-AC85U += MODEM=y PRINTER=y APP="network" WEBDAV=y 
  SMARTSYNCBASE=y TIMEMACHINE=y

export RT-AC65U := $(RT-AC85U_BASE)
export RT-AC65U += BASE_MODEL="RT-AC85U" BUILD_NAME="RT-AC65U" 
  EXTRA_KERNEL_CONFIGS="MT7621_BAUDRATE=57600 RT2880_DRAM_128M=y 
  UBOOT_CMDLINE=y MODEL_RTAC65U=y RTAC65U=y SMART_CARRIER_SENSE_SUPPORT=y 
  MT_DFS_SUPPORT=y DUAL_TRX=y FIRST_IF_IPAELNA=y SECOND_IF_IPAELNA=y"
export RT-AC65U += APP="none" NO_FTP=y
}} ===See also=== *[[ASUS RT-AC86U]] - AC2900 Dual Band Wireless Gigabit Router *[[ASUS RT-AC85U]] - AC2600 Dual Band Wireless Gigabit Router *'''[[ASUS RT-AC65U]]''' - AC1900 Dual Band Wireless Gigabit Router *[[ASUS RT-AC58U]] - AC1200 Dual Band Wireless Gigabit Router *[[ASUS RT-AC53]] - AC750 Dual Band Wireless Gigabit Router *[[ASUS RT-AC1200GU]] - AC1200 Dual Band Wireless Gigabit Router __NOTOC__
